## MÓDULO 14 — PIPELINE CI/CD DE SEGURIDAD

Crear `.github/workflows/security.yml`:

```yaml
name: Security Pipeline

on: [push, pull_request]

jobs:
  security-scan:
    runs-on: ubuntu-latest
    steps:
      - uses: actions/checkout@v4

      - name: Set up Python
        uses: actions/setup-python@v5
        with:
          python-version: '3.11'

      - name: Install security tools
        run: pip install bandit pip-audit safety pytest

      - name: Static analysis (Bandit)
        run: bandit -r backend/ -ll -ii --exclude backend/venv,backend/tests -f json -o bandit-report.json
        continue-on-error: false

      - name: Dependency vulnerability scan (pip-audit)
        run: pip-audit -r backend/requirements.txt --format json -o pip-audit-report.json

      - name: Run security tests
        run: cd backend && pytest tests/test_security.py -v --tb=short
        env:
          JWT_SECRET: ${{ secrets.JWT_SECRET_TEST }}
          ENCRYPTION_MASTER_KEY: ${{ secrets.ENCRYPTION_KEY_TEST }}

      - name: Check for secrets in code (gitleaks)
        uses: gitleaks/gitleaks-action@v2
        env:
          GITHUB_TOKEN: ${{ secrets.GITHUB_TOKEN }}

      - name: Upload security reports
        uses: actions/upload-artifact@v4
        if: always()
        with:
          name: security-reports
          path: |
            bandit-report.json
            pip-audit-report.json
```

